cs.NE, cs.DS, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY 

The paper discusses parameter control in the context of evolutionary algorithms, which are commonly used in optimization problems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also deals with running-time analysis, which suggests that it could belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) or cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper proposes an updated classification scheme for parameter control, which could place it in cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
